### Test Authorization API (RBAC)
@host = https://localhost:5001

### 1. Login sebagai USER biasa
# @name loginUser
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Ambil Token User
@userToken = {{loginUser.response.body.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### 2. Login sebagai MANAGER
# @name loginManager
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "manager@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Ambil Token Manager
@managerToken = {{loginManager.response.body.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### 3. Login sebagai ADMIN
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Ambil Token Admin
@adminToken = {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.tokens.accessToken}}


### ==============================================
### TEST RBAC ENDPOINTS
### ==============================================

### 4. Akses Dashboard (Boleh Admin & Manager, dilarang untuk User)
### Pake Token User (Harusnya 403 Forbidden)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### Pake Token Manager (Harusnya 200 OK)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}


### 5. Akses Laporan Keuangan (HANYA Admin)
### Pake Token Manager (Harusnya 403 Forbidden)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{managerToken}}

### Pake Token Admin (Harusnya 200 OK)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/reports
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### 6. Akses Publik (Tidak perlu token)
### Harusnya 200 OK (meski tanpa Authorization header)
GET {{host}}/api/admin/public-info
